episodes.title: Inside the California Trans Cult Behind Four Murders
episodes.description:
A transgender radical cult in California is reportedly behind four recent murders: Two in Pennsylvania, one in Vermont, and one in California. The name of the cult is the Zizians.

The Zizians are a radical offshoot of the rationalist movement in the Bay Area. Rationalism dates back to Descartes and has recently experienced a resurgence in Silicon Valley, attracting adherents like Sam Bankman-Fried and funders like Peter Thiel. Ziz, the leader of the eponymous Zizians, started beefing with the rationalists at Berkeley and formed her own cult: One that was vegan, transgender, and... violent. 

This video investigates the Zizians, their history, and the spree of murders they're allegedly behind.
